<div type="abstract"><head>Peter Volckamer an Heinrich von Aufseß</head><p>Der Absender teilt mit, dass der Rat Jobst Peler trotz des vormals nicht genutzten Geleits bis Walpurgistag drei Tage Geleit gewährt, um ihn anzuhören.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_426" id="212r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_426_r1l24"><expan>Rıtt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Aufſeſʒ </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_426_line_1577283255548_7160">
<add><ab facs="#facs_426_line_1577283237657_7149">Meın <expan>wıllıg</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_426_line_1577283239625_7154">dıenſt beuor </ab></add> <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> als Jr mir <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / von Jobs Pelers </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_426_r1l27"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc / das han ıch wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd han mıt meinen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_426_r1l28"><expan>freẅnd<ex>en</ex></expan> dauon geredt / an den vernym ıch daʒ ſıe dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_426_r1l29"><expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Jobs Peler . vormals . geleyt ʒu Jn ʒu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒugeſagt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_426_r1l30">vnd auch <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> darnach ʒugeſchrıben haben . Jn </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_427" id="212v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_427_r1l1"><expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ʒeıt ſey er ʒu Jn niht <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> . VVıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſo han ıch mıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_427_r1l2"><expan>meine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>freẅnd<ex>en</ex></expan> vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſou<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> geredt / wenn <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> peler </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_427_r1l3"><expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> ſand <expan>walp<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>en</ex></expan> tag ſchıerıſt . ʒu Jn gen <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_427_r1l4">wıl . ſo ſol er ʒu vnd von Jn für ſıe vnd dıe Jren on geuerde </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_427_r1l5">drey tag geleyt haben ſo wellen ſıe ſein rede denn <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_427_line_1577283278495_7187">Denn wo ıch <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_427_r1l8"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_427_r1l9"><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> volkmeır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_427_r1l10">ʒu <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_426" id="212r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Ritt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Aufsesz</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><add>Mein <expan>willig</expan> dienst bevor</add>.
                            <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir mir
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Jobs Pelers
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das han ich wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und han mit meinen
                                <expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan> davon geredt; an den vernym ich,
                        daz sie dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Jobs Peler vormals geleyt zu
                        in zu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> zugesagt und auch
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> darnach zugeschriben haben, in <pb facs="#facs_427" id="212v"/>
<expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> zeit sey er zu in niht
                                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>. Wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so
                        han ich mit <expan>meine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan> umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>sov<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> geredt, wenn
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Peler
        <expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> <app><note><q type="date">sand
                <expan>Walp<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>en</ex></expan> tag schierist</q>01.05.1422</note></app> zu in gen
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wil, so sol er zu und von in für sie und die
                        iren on geverde drey tag geleyt haben, so wellen sie sein rede denn
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören. Denn wo ich
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.<lb/><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        Volkmeir zu <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
</div></body>
